<br>
I've liked Clive Barker's material for a long time, first movie I saw was Hellraiser, and went down the line from Night Breed, Lord of Illusions, among others.  I've read quite a few of his books, and find they wonderfuly detailed and full of imagenation.  It was really nice to see he decided to work on a video game with all of his ideas and creations in it.  There are screenshots, etc. and a demo.  <br>
<br>
The detail is great, I am one for blood and gore, and this demo did it for me, really liked it a lot, there are eerie sounds and ghostly apparitions.  The story line is wonderful, quite a few different spells and weapons to use, and one is able to upgrade the spells so that they are more powerful.  I am really looking forward to buying this game for my birthday and going into it.  I hope he works on more material like this, it was really great.<br>
<br>
Anyways  hope some of you guys check out this demo, I really enjoyed it, and hope you do as well.<br>
<br>
